name: Beguda wanna be a birdie!
description:
This game was made within 4 hours as a challenge I took.

This is a Flappy Bird clone.

Beguda always dreamt to soar high like a bird this is his day!

Made by me (Kovid Khokar/Silva Khokar/ 1111Someone11)

Note- My laptop has a 1366*768 screen so it was made by keeping that in mind. Problems might emerge if you have a full HD screen.
